  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2128810/extras/35b51e3f46bc288ceb500203ffdec532.avif?t=1774005016\" width=600 height=125 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > <strong>Dinosaurs Dominion</strong> is built around <strong>combat</strong>, <strong>exploration</strong>, and <strong>progression</strong>. Inspired by roguelites, each journey is its own run where progress comes from exploration and conquest.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2128810/extras/37482c3be9e358b4d843e62b0272f4ef.avif?t=1774005016\" width=616 height=36 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2128810/extras/0b6768a761d1b1902e0fd74bd9e910e0.poster.avif?t=1774005016\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2128810/extras/0b6768a761d1b1902e0fd74bd9e910e0.webm?t=1774005016\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2128810/extras/0b6768a761d1b1902e0fd74bd9e910e0.mp4?t=1774005016\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Face rivals in personal, high-stakes <strong>one-on-one combat</strong>. Each fight is a test of timing, spacing, and skill. Patience is rewarded while recklessness is punished. You must stay alert and wait for the right moment to strike.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2128810/extras/e13322d9440079dd9a0f6c4f1467706e.avif?t=1774005016\" width=616 height=36 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2128810/extras/2e389ccb90c9f91d4c750c7386325a32.poster.avif?t=1774005016\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2128810/extras/2e389ccb90c9f91d4c750c7386325a32.webm?t=1774005016\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2128810/extras/2e389ccb90c9f91d4c750c7386325a32.mp4?t=1774005016\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Roam freely across <strong>diverse biomes</strong>, from lush forests to ashen wastes and snow-covered cliffs. Uncover secrets, discover ancient landmarks, and unlock new species as you explore. Each region tells its own story, and every step brings you closer to reclaiming the wild.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2128810/extras/6ef85795ca4f6008c2c7cd8f4a94e9c6.avif?t=1774005016\" width=616 height=36 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2128810/extras/cadee757bbe83994fd5e13283010fee0.poster.avif?t=1774005016\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2128810/extras/cadee757bbe83994fd5e13283010fee0.webm?t=1774005016\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2128810/extras/cadee757bbe83994fd5e13283010fee0.mp4?t=1774005016\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Unlock mutations</strong> that suit your playstyle and sharpen your instincts with each victory, while defeat returns you to the start.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2128810/extras/506cf160148ac709a5576a6b2ad9cf05.avif?t=1774005016\" width=616 height=36 /></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>14 playable dinosaurs</strong>, from the nimble Austroraptor to the towering Tyrannosaurus, each with a playstyle defined by size, power, and mobility.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>13 mutations</strong> that let you evolve, specialize, and experiment.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>3 open-world maps</strong>, each with unique biomes and environmental storytelling.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Focused <strong>one on one combat</strong> inspired by Souls-like design.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Roguelite progression</strong> with single-run challenges and permanent impact across journeys.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Landmarks</strong>, Relics, and Echoes that reward exploration with meaningful discoveries.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Totems and Trophies</strong>, unlockable rewards that reveal deeper insights into the world.</p></li></ul>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2128810/extras/35b51e3f46bc288ceb500203ffdec532.avif?t=1774005016\" width=600 height=125 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > <strong>Dinosaurs Dominion</strong> is built around <strong>combat</strong>, <strong>exploration</strong>, and <strong>progression</strong>. Inspired by roguelites, each journey is its own run where progress comes from exploration and conquest.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2128810/extras/37482c3be9e358b4d843e62b0272f4ef.avif?t=1774005016\" width=616 height=36 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2128810/extras/0b6768a761d1b1902e0fd74bd9e910e0.poster.avif?t=1774005016\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2128810/extras/0b6768a761d1b1902e0fd74bd9e910e0.webm?t=1774005016\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2128810/extras/0b6768a761d1b1902e0fd74bd9e910e0.mp4?t=1774005016\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Face rivals in personal, high-stakes <strong>one-on-one combat</strong>. Each fight is a test of timing, spacing, and skill. Patience is rewarded while recklessness is punished. You must stay alert and wait for the right moment to strike.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2128810/extras/e13322d9440079dd9a0f6c4f1467706e.avif?t=1774005016\" widt