 playstyle and sharpen your instincts with each victory, while defeat returns you to the start.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2128810/extras/506cf160148ac709a5576a6b2ad9cf05.avif?t=1774005016\" width=616 height=36 /></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>14 playable dinosaurs</strong>, from the nimble Austroraptor to the towering Tyrannosaurus, each with a playstyle defined by size, power, and mobility.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>13 mutations</strong> that let you evolve, specialize, and experiment.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>3 open-world maps</strong>, each with unique biomes and environmental storytelling.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Focused <strong>one on one combat</strong> inspired by Souls-like design.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Roguelite progression</strong> with single-run challenges and permanent impact across journeys.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Landmarks</strong>, Relics, and Echoes that reward exploration with meaningful discoveries.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Totems and Trophies</strong>, unlockable rewards that reveal deeper insights into the world.</p></li></ul>",
